If you start out as a private
company and you want to get

01:02:55.370 --> 01:02:58.820
listed on the stock exchange,
that's called going public.

01:02:58.820 --> 01:03:03.450
When you go public, the SEC is
on your back and it says, you

01:03:03.450 --> 01:03:07.220
