If the company were
selling for $5

01:09:03.225 --> 01:09:05.520
billion, I might do that.

01:09:05.520 --> 01:09:06.640
Well, not me.

01:09:06.640 --> 01:09:10.590
Somebody who arranges these
things could do that.

01:09:10.590 --> 01:09:12.640
So, I buy the company
for $5 billion.

01:09:12.640 --> 01:09:14.670
I tell everybody, you're
all fired.

01:09:14.670 --> 01:09:16.189
We're going out of business.

